            "section_rank": 11
        },
        {
            "text": "Figure 2: The two off-axis cones centered at \u00b1 \u03c0 2 away in \u03c6 and at the same \u03b7 relative to a given jet.",
            "section": "Figure 2 :",
            "paragraph_rank": 14,
